title: DJ Silviomanuel-Interactive Progression First Dose 2008 noneofur
description:
WTF is an interactive DJ Mix?

have you ever wished in the middle of a mix to let it end or going on another way? this mix collection is exactly about that. 
you have 3 Intro mixes and 4 Outro mixes. you put them into a playlist of a player like itunes or winamp or vlc or whatever. play the first intro mix you want do listen to and as long as it lasts, you have time to decide what's coming next - ANY Outro mix! some mp3-players have an option to make a playlist on the go. this can be useful too on the road.

so, when playback, it's always Intro-Outro, that means you have almost 8 hours of mixed music that can be combined in 3x4=12 different ways!

the musical styles vary from minimalhouse/techno ambient mixes (subversive, floating together), to house in many styles (mi Casa..., the House of the Smile), house-, nu-, whatever-break (Zen Garden), techno and harder struff (Brutal Truth) and Trance. 

I know the guy who made this mix and I have to say he did an amazing job: most of the time you listen to at least 2 tracks at once, but sometimes 3, 4, or even 5 tracks are played at one time!!! I couldnt believe when I saw what I heard! beside that, 90% of the tracks are 2008 releases, which means that these tracks will be the soundtrack for this season. so dl, listen, enjoy, tell your friends and seeeeeed!!

and here's the tracklist:
